      <div type="commentary">
        <p>The inscription is incomplete. <ptr target="bib:Mahalingam1988_01"/> notes: <quote>Probably a few more letters are wanting. The significance of these names is not clear. They were probably the <hi rend="italic">taḷi uḍaiyār</hi> (temple priests), as stated in l. 13.</quote></p>
        <p>According to <ptr target="bib:Mahalingam1988_01"/>: <quote>This gives the earliest reference to the setting up of the image of god Ganapati, during the Pallava period.</quote></p>
      </div>
